name: Contemporary Photography NOW Catalogue
description:
Limited edition exhibition catalogue for our annual photography open show 'Contemporary Photography NOW'. 

Featuring works by all 13 selected artists and an insight into their practice. Plus an introduction and essay from the exhibitions team at Surface Gallery.

Produced as a limited edition run of 100, and individually hand numbered, these catalogues have been digitally printed on traditional newspaper.

All the money we make from the sale of these catalogues goes towards the running of the gallery and enables us to work on making publications for future exhibitions.

Shipped via Royal Mail first class. Alternatively, you can pick up a copy from the gallery space.

name: Tote Bags
description:
Colourful hand screenprinted tote bags on 100% cotton. We have a limited number of these, with only a few of some colours left!

Available in blue, green, orange, and red.

The money we make from the sale of these goes to help with our everyday running costs of the gallery. 

Shipped via Royal Mail First Class postage.
